<body><p class="body">The goal of this was to explore the idea of how well mentos and soda react.  We chose 3 different flavors of mentos and three different types of soda.  We found you didn't need to use the entire package of mentos, but if you could manage it, then go for it.  Also, use pepsi and mint mentos because it had a faster reaction with more potential to explode.  Note: should pour about 2 cups of liquid out first to allow for more time to replace cap.</p>
